---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Xiaochang Miao"
  description="About this blog and the kinds of technical notes published here."
>
  <section class="page-intro">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Why this site exists.</h1>
    <p class="hero-copy">
      This is where I write down technical lessons before they get rounded off
      into vague memory.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="page-block prose-block">
    <p>
      The writing here is meant to stay practical. Some posts will be proper
      walkthroughs, but many should only do one job well: capture a useful point
      clearly.
    </p>
    <p>
      The main topics are machine learning, large language models, retrieval,
      ranking systems, infrastructure, and engineering workflow. If something is
      interesting but still half-formed, it can still belong here as a note.
    </p>
    <p>
      The publishing standard is intentionally low. If a note explains the
      problem, the failed intuition, and the lesson I would want next time, it
      is probably worth posting.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
